# KVB Rénovation Site

- This is a static GitHub Pages site for KVB Rénovation, served from the repository root.
- Production domain is `https://kvb-renovation.fr/`; keep `CNAME`, canonical URL, Open Graph URL, and JSON-LD URL aligned.
- Edit business content in `content.json` when possible; `main.js` loads it at runtime.
- Keep contact privacy behavior intact: the email may be used by JavaScript contact flows, but should not be visibly printed in `index.html` or JSON-LD unless `publishEmailInSchema` is explicitly changed.
- Run `node ./scripts/validate.mjs` after changes that touch HTML, content, JavaScript, deployment, or SEO metadata.
